```json
{
  "application": "SourceSelector",
  "software": [
    "SourceSelector",
    "Singularity",
    "Caesar"
  ],
  "resources": [
    "input file (.root)",
    "cut file (ascii)",
    "environment file (.sh)",
    "container image (.simg)",
    "batch system (PBS/SLURM)"
  ],
  "requirements": [
    "CAESAR_DIR environment variable",
    "access to batch system (if submitting jobs)"
  ],
  "arguments": [
    "--filelist=[FILELIST]",
    "--inputfile=[FILENAME]",
    "--cutfile=[CUTFILE]",
    "--envfile=[ENV_FILE]",
    "--loglevel=[LOG_LEVEL]",
    "--maxfiles=[NMAX_PROCESSED_FILES]",
    "--addrunindex",
    "--outdir=[OUTPUT_DIR]",
    "--containerrun",
    "--containerimg=[CONTAINER_IMG]",
    "--containeroptions=[CONTAINER_OPTIONS]",
    "--submit",
    "--batchsystem=[BATCH_SYSTEM]",
    "--queue=[BATCH_QUEUE]",
    "--jobwalltime=[JOB_WALLTIME]",
    "--jobcpus=[JOB_NCPUS]",
    "--jobnodes=[JOB_NNODES]",
    "--jobmemory=[JOB_MEMORY]",
    "--jobusergroup=[JOB_USER_GROUP]"
  ]
}
```
